l:dependency.name: Init Pipeline Jenkins Plugin
l:dependency.l:description: Requires the Git Plugin. This plugin listens alongside the Git Plugin. In cases where Jenkins does NOT have the pipeline referenced by the notifyCommit configured, InitPipeline calls an external golang binary to instantiate and build the pipeline. The plugin only acts in the case where the job doesn't already exist
